==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Dracontic
<hw>Dra*con"tic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[From L.
<ets>draco</ets> dragon, in allusion to the terms <ets>dragon's
head</ets> and <ets>dragon's tail</ets>.]</ety> <fld>(Astron.)</fld>
<def>Belonging to that space of time in which the moon performs one
revolution, from ascending node to ascending node. See <cref>Dragon's
head</cref>, under <er>Dragon</er>.</def> <mark>[Obs.]</mark>
⟦ldquo⟧<xex>Dracontic</xex> month.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Crabb.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Dracontine</ent>⟦br⟧
